#1 Positive paravaginal mass
#2 History of grade 1 endometrial cancer treated in 2005
For exploration tomorrow, we will begin in synchronous position and do some vaginal biopsies to be sure there is no mucosal disease and then proceed with midline and dissection of the paravaginal mass with resection.  Listed as such, possible bowel resection, possible portion of bladder resection.  However, this is a localized lesion.  I did not anticipate a major debulking operation.  Discussed with the patient and her husband.  Reviewed all risks, benefits, and alternatives.  Patient signed consent in clinic today.  She should not need site marking as this procedure list is excision of a mass.  All questions answered.

